<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>kubernetes on Aiden's Deep Machine Learning lab</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/categories/kubernetes/</link><description>Recent content in kubernetes on Aiden's Deep Machine Learning lab</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><copyright>Copyright © 2020-2021, Aiden Jeon; all rights reserved.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Mar 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/categories/kubernetes/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>kubernetes에서 ghcr package pull 하기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/kubernetes/kubernetes_ghcr/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Mar 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/kubernetes/kubernetes_ghcr/</guid><description>
&lt;p>kubernetes 에서 사용하는 image는 기본적으로 dockerhub에서 pull 된다. 기본적으로 Local에 있는 패키지는 사용하지 않는다.
회사에서는 도커 이미지를 dockerhub와 같은 곳에 public 하게 공유할 수가 없다.
그래서 github 에서 제공하는 (GHCR) GitHub Container Registry for Docker images 을 이용해서 도커 이미지를 관리하고 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>GHCR 을 이용하기 위해서는 github access key 가 필요하다. 우선 github access token을 발급 받아 보자.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="1-ghcr-을-위한-github-access-token-발급-받기">1. ghcr 을 위한 github access token 발급 받기&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>우선 github setting에서 deplotver settings / personal access tokens 로 들어간다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/0.png" alt="img">
여기서 generate new token을 누른다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/1.png" alt="img">
토큰 이름으로 ghcr-token을 입력하고 packages와 관련된 권한을 주고 token을 생성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/2.png" alt="img">
다음과 같이 토큰이 생성된다. 이제 이 토큰을 잘 저장해둔다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-kubernetes-secret">2. kubernetes secret&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>다음으로 kubernetes 에 secret 을 생성해준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl -n &amp;lt;k8s-namespace&amp;gt; create secret docker-registry &amp;lt;k8s-docker-registry-secret-name&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-server&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ghcr.io &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-username&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-username&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-password&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-personal-access-token&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-email&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;email-address&amp;gt;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>k8s-docker-registry-secret-name&lt;/code>: secret 이름&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>github-username&lt;/code>: github 유저 네임&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>github-personal-access-token&lt;/code>: 발급받은 토큰&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>email-address&lt;/code>: github 이메일&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>예를 들면 아래와 같이 사용할 수 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl -n default create secret docker-registry test-ghcr &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-server&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ghcr.io &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-username&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>aiden-jeon &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-password&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-personal-access-token&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-email&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ells2124@gmail.com
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 실행될 경우 아래와 같이 출력된다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>secret/test-ghcr created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="3-yaml-파일-작성">3. yaml 파일 작성&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>이제 deployment를 위한 yaml 파일을 작성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">apps/v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Deployment&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">selector&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">matchLabels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">containers&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">ghcr.io/{user-name}/{package-name}:{package-tag}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">imagePullPolicy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Always&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ports&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">containerPort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">imagePullSecrets&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">23&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-ghcr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>image에 ghcr 의 도커 이미지를 입력해주면 된다.
그리고 imagePullSecrets에 좀 전에 생성한 secret 의 이름을 입력하면 된다.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>